    {
      "id": "minimum-library-template-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Contract Note",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 820,
        "y": -210
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Minimum Library Shape\n\nThis template exists for graphs whose primary job is to **republish reusable artifacts**.\n\nRequired parts:\n\n- declaration with `targetMode: library`\n- title\n- type-definition\n- one root-facing view\n- explicit export bridges\n- one note explaining what the library contains\n\nThe library root is identity and browsing surface. The export bridges are the reusable vocabulary."
      }
    },
